---
title: Mango and Passion Fruit Smoothie Bowl serves 2
description: A smoothie bowl is an amazing way to add more fruit to your diet. This recipe contains mango, passion fruit, blueberries and a scattering of granola for a nice crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R4002_W22_IE_IEA40341-2_Main_high-4eacff0a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/67cb19d6849ab09a45ce298f-en-IE.pdf
cuisine: European
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 433 kcal
  fat: 22.5 g
  saturated fat: 17.1 g
  carbohydrates: 51.6 g
