servings: 2
---

Halve the @passion fruit{1}.

Peel the @mango{1} and remove the pit. Chop into 1cm pieces.

Blend the mango with @coconut milk{1%pack} and @yoghurt{110%g} in a #blender{}.

Loosen with a splash of @water{to taste} and add @sugar{to taste}, if required.

Divide the smoothie between #bowls{}.

Top with the passion fruit halves, @blueberries{125%g} and @granola{60%g}.